Please change globs to the nexpose version we are dealing with.

0. git clone git://github.com/bperry-r7/Nexpose-Install-Scripts.git
1. cd Nexpose-Install-Scripts/
2. mkdir nexpose*/tmp
3. wget http://download2.rapid7.com/download/NeXpose-v4/NeXposeSetup-Linux64.bin *amd64/tmp
4. wget http://download2.rapid7.com/download/NeXpose-v4/NeXposeSetup-Linux32.bin *i386/tmp
5. dpkg-deb --build nexpose*


